{"tid":1511512,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"乃木坂46討論區#224：佐々木琴子お誕生日おめでとうございます！","createTime":"2019-08-27T14:24:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-09T03:07:00.000Z","uid":262434,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"d47d941d85b10ef9a44f524aca6fe0e972bb493c","tid":1511512,"uid":262434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T14:24:10.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>乃Po呼籲:</strong></span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong> 🎂琴子21歲生日快樂🎂<br />\n鳴謝南音琴推yui仔🍎<br />\n</strong></span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cu178O9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCu178O9.jpg&h=a1edcbdd&s={SIZE}\" /></strong></span></span></div><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">乃木坂46(Nogizaka46)</span> 是一個日本大型女子偶像團體，為另一著名女子團體AKB48的「官方對手／正式對手」（公式ライバル），因此其行銷策略與AKB48的姐妹團體&mdash;&mdash;SKE48、NMB48、HKT48等不同，但總製作人同樣是秋元康，且與其他姊妹團體之間仍常有跨團體的合作或競賽企畫。團體名字中的「46」讀作「Forty-six／フォーティシックス」，而不是讀作「四十六／よんじゅうろく」。包含一期生,二期生,三期生以及四期生在內，團體目前共有46名成員，而隊長為櫻井玲香。<br />\n乃木坂46是作為AKB48的「官方對手」而成立的女子團體，因此跟AKB48的「姊妹團體」（如SKE48等）不同。例如團體不像AKB48及其姊妹團體般擁有AKB48劇場、NMB48劇場等專屬表演場地。團體名稱中的「乃木坂」是唱片公司日本索尼音樂（SME）總部大樓的所在地。<br />\n根據秋元康所說，<span style=\"color: red;\">「46」象徵：「就算人數比AKB48少，也具有不遜於AKB48的幹勁</span>」。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">成員名單:</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nogizaka46.com/member/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nogizaka46.com%2Fmember%2F&d=hq0sVSmFYzKD%2BASQGeqgxsFcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=a84a3296\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nogizaka46.com/member/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">-NEWS-</div><br />\n</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">乃木坂46 24thシングル<br />\n「夜明けまで強がらなくてもいい」<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">9月4日發售</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EeYNpoM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEeYNpoM.png&h=1c0202b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n乃木坂46 23rdシングル<br />\n「Sing Out！」<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">發售中</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0cipwn6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0cipwn6.jpg&h=c51edcbb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n乃木坂46 4thアルバム<br />\n「今が思い出になるまで」<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">發售中</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LdMnh3x.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLdMnh3x.jpg&h=f6ef5b5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">斉藤優里1st写真集「7秒のしあわせ」 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">發售中</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UEdWQYN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUEdWQYN.png&h=e5c86eda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">映畫「Hot Gimmick: Girl Meets Boy」<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">上映中</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5XcXAn7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5XcXAn7.jpg&h=de229448&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">『いつのまにか、ここにいる Documentary of 乃木坂46』<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">上映中</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uujOG31.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuujOG31.png&h=445c7414&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">乃木坂46成員列表 23RD VER.(最新)</span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9vaCRpX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9vaCRpX.png&h=006e8631&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">乃木坂46 四期生</span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/NjUnHMj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FNjUnHMj.jpg&h=61687ed4&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">歡迎新人加入</span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://nogizaka46-dc.com/sort/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnogizaka46-dc.com%2Fsort%2F&d=hq0sVSmFYzKD%2BASQGeqgxsFcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=6e5d109a\" target=\"_blank\">http://nogizaka46-dc.com/sort/</a></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://andykwanfai.github.io/nogizaka46-sort/#/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fandykwanfai.github.io%2Fnogizaka46-sort%2F%23%2F&d=hq0sVSmFYzKD%2BASQGeqgxsFcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=5f98b580\" target=\"_blank\">https://andykwanfai.github.io/nogizaka46-sort/#/</a></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請新/舊手足定期體檢，以便加入DD黨</span></span></div><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Q&amp;A</div></span></span><br />\n1）那乃木坂乃何許人也？<br />\n簡單來說，乃木坂是來自日本的偶像組合，演戲唱歌跳舞等全部都會參與，是正統全能型偶像。<br />\n<br />\n2）那裡可以購買乃木坂既有關產品（生寫、CD、海報、寫真集、演唱會等）？<br />\n一般來說，信和地庫會有存貨，不過價錢就...另外有不少商品需於官方WEBSHOP購入，不過這裡有機會提供代購,，要看看手足們的心情。<br />\n<br />\n3）這裡可否討論其他非46的成員？<br />\n我們一般不會阻止，但請適量討論。皆因這裡主要討論46GRP,你也可作理性討論，攻擊、黑其他成員,但請先作好世界大戰的準備。<br />\n<br />\n4）那麼我要如何見到乃木坂成員？<br />\n直接飛去日本參加握手會、演唱會，但不要幻想他會再來港，因香港已經柒出國際。詳細辦法請向手足查詢。<br />\n<br />\n5）除了46GRP,有什麼值得推薦？<br />\n二期四姊妹<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gUi1rBs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgUi1rBs.jpg&h=d4133f41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5zYdhH8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5zYdhH8.jpg&h=4aedacd7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">TEMPLATE:</span></span><br />\n<del>[url]https: //<a href=\"http://docs.google.com/document/d/17WaT3I7dwYQdmaT85JQnAJAzfBc9EXMXLKGLlpllO2E/edit?usp=sharing[/url]\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fdocument%2Fd%2F17WaT3I7dwYQdmaT85JQnAJAzfBc9EXMXLKGLlpllO2E%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing%5B%2Furl%5D&d=hq0sVSmFYzKD%2BASQGeqgxsFcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=ddc2ee15\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">docs.google.com/document/d/17WaT3I7dwYQdmaT85JQnAJAzfBc9EXMXLKGLlpllO2E/edit?usp=sharing[/url]</a></del><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ns1NdRm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNs1NdRm.png&h=61cb3eef&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"f704383b7db95e94c87f58c962aa76e505433e08","tid":1511512,"uid":230890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T14:24:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"10ff261a801112d39a87d1e4f9431140ec3a77b6","tid":1511512,"uid":51594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T14:25:30.000Z","msg":"琴子生日快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n補翻想1001嗰張<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4f90d4d6d0989f2c7eb92879b2a7b27e4cf8559","tid":1511512,"uid":35758,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T14:25:36.000Z","msg":"乃po手足唔識計數"},{"pid":"e9b360b2428fc7b38721e0bade1c29550d8bf680","tid":